{"tid":2025951,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"律政司：岑敖暉文章涉嫌煽動暴力，違反禁制令！","createTime":"2020-05-20T15:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T16:23:49.000Z","uid":219007,"like":38,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4e66d20562085e95a5b3201d1bab052d88020935","tid":2025951,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:12:54.000Z","msg":"【再收律政司恐嚇信】<br />\n<br />\n上星期五收到黑警恐嚇信，今天到律政司：指我指控警察謀殺周梓樂的文章涉嫌「促進、鼓勵或煽動暴力」，「違反法庭禁制令」，並要求我在七天內移除該文章。<br />\n<br />\n看來政權真的好想以言入罪：黑警恐嚇不成，今日就換律政司。坦白說，我收到信之後，都有想過他們真的可能會進行起訴，會不會靜靜雞del post就算，但再想一想，如果我們習慣這樣的行為會「犯法」、習慣「以言入罪」是「常態」，那麼不但這個政權可怕，我們的「習慣」和「退縮」也頗恐怖的。<br />\n<br />\n廿三條還未立法，指出黑警犯罪，何罪之有？<br />\n對手足表示不割席，何罪之有？<br />\n<br />\n因此本人對律政司要求的回應如下：<br />\n<br />\nNoted with thanks.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ORLUPyy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FORLUPyy.jpg&h=41ce878f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v3J7p6Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv3J7p6Z.jpg&h=49211f0a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61d627895cf7ce5986ffbf600269ecaa05ddd3d4","tid":2025951,"uid":280329,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:17:05.000Z","msg":"睇黎呢個月中共好撚急<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba4541233dc1496dc1c5c535aba7988d8eee4b3","tid":2025951,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:17:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8bb3a6929d501abafcaf10eeb4f408f110dd5f","tid":2025951,"uid":355793,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:18:03.000Z","msg":"哪裡煽動了暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n提出質疑就煽動暴力？<br />\n應該係黑警太常用暴力，所以先會覺得人地講句野都煽動到暴力"},{"pid":"77f6ccd9b4